title: Selig on U.S.-China Trade
itunes:title: Selig on U.S.-China Trade
description:
Stefan Selig, Managing Partner at BridgePark Advisors, discusses the U.S.-China trade war. He says the relationship between the U.S. and China is under increasing duress.

Hosts: Jason Kelly and Paul Sweeney. Producer: Doni Holloway.
